General.Name: Hedera Group publ AB
General.Description: Hedera Group AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, provides personal assistance, staffing, and recruitment services for healthcare and social care sectors in Sweden. It offers recruitment services for doctors, nurses, occupational therapists, midwives, sociologists psychologists, and physiotherapists. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden. Hedera Group AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Bertil Haglund med bolag.
